item.title: 10 years using the MacBook Pro 9,2
item.description: The MacBook Pro 9,2 is a model of the MacBook Pro that was released in June 2012.Â It has a 13.3-inch display, a 2.5 GHz or 2.9 GHz dual-core Intel Core i5 or i7 processor, 4 GB or 8 GB of RAM, and a 500 GB or 750 GB hard drive. My MacBook was bought around 2013 or 2014, don’t remember exactly. It was bought new, with 4GB of RAM and 500 GB hard drive.
